 was quite an event, all the - clean clothes were put out but I was - thought you might be interested in the one bath a week. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 And the water used to be an awful shemozzle. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
