Yes we did. Yes, yes, that's what I've been thinking. Looking back, we - we all came home on the one five train from Leicester, and caught a quart
er to something back to school in the afternoon, and - or up to hockey, but we always came - father, all of us came home for midday meal. Yes, yes.
