f meat or perhaps I didn't like meat, but always very good - vegetables - and meat and gravy. And always a pudding. Or if it wasn't pudding it was oranges, we seemed to eat thousands of oranges. What I remember is we had such a lot of butter. It used to c
ome eight pound a week you see in a big cardboard thing, and - lot of butter, I don't remember we had a lot if meat.
