he people who lived round us were - you know, we were all the same sort. And then perhaps going to school by train there were those who went to our school and the others, who }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 didn\rquote t}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Could you tell me who the others were who weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 Well of course we thought - we were the cat's whiskers who went to - the Wiggy. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Then there were the Alderman Newton's and the other school, but - we didn't really mix with any others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What group would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I don't know, sort of professional middle class.
