Nearly all much of muchness. I - Dorothy Smith's father ran a - a clothing - very prosperous clothing shop in Leicester. But - oh and then Olga Donaldson, her father was - Cannon Donaldson you see, at the Vicarage at St Mark}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6301663\charrsid11354935 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 s. My other friend, Yvette Stibby, her father, in the first world war became a milliona}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 re. And - the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 Goddard\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935  - the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 Goddard\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935  plate powder, Bobby Goddard and all that lot.
