were jolly nice girls too. But - I happened to meet a girl called Herrington the other day and I said, oh I knew some Herrington's in Leicester, the shop you see, we didn't know them personally, she said, oh were they in trade? I said, yes, jolly good tra
de.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Who did the clergy associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
Well they weren't very popular at Burstall. There was a - - the headmaster at the boys school, Jimmy Went, lived at Burstall you see and he was thought a lot of. But - the Vicar - oh Brook-Brown, one or two 
of the Vicars we liked very much but later on - after the war, they were a poor lot. Before the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Who did the teachers associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well - my teachers at our school, they were a very fine lot. Sort of old Leicester families, I don't think 
they were terribly highly qualified. Later on they were coming in from - Oxford and Cambridge you see, sort of - fine young things, but those who taught me - they were our own sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So who would they mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Everybody, County and all the rest of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What about farmers, do you know anything about them, who they associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Farmers - I should think they stuck together mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 And employers, who did they associate with?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Golf club. Each other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I should say the nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 And chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Same. Same thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 In some places there was a great social division between church and chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I don't think there was. No, not - not then, not like there is in villages and that. Not - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Where we lived, the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you know about that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
No, I remember - when Bib had scarlet fever I went into rooms in Leicester with - Auntie Emily. I thought they were lovely, they had meals in the kitchen. All very friendly and nice. That I think is my - really only experience with -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 You couldn't sort of put them into groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No. No. No.-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you meet your maids' families or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
I think when we were terribly little, very little. But you see travelling was difficult and they mostly came from - places like Colville and that sort of thing, well you couldn't get to Colville from Leicester.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you know if some families were thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes, there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Not really, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did your mother and father have the same attitude as each other to people in different social classes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes, but - I - mother was a bit snobby but father would respect a very good workman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So they were a bit different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Little bit different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well I think probably it would be her early life you know, sort of coming from America to England and back to Am
erica and that sort of thing, and - her people really - had once been - better than - more - I won't say money but - but had something about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So you think she was basing this really on her parents rather than the work or the house or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 It was what was behind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes. I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Can you remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Not when I was very young. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Can you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well I just thought father was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 You can't say why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No, well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What was the definition of a real gentleman in your mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well in my mind it had nothing to do with money. Money didn't enter
 in - into our lives really. We didn't think of people as having money but - you know. We might even despise them if they were too moneyed. We had an instinctive feeling - as children, I don't know how.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember anyone being described as a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Not then. I have my own ideas now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 But not at that time when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 We liked them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When you were naughty did your mother ever say, I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How did the policeman treat the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 The policeman treated? I think-they were out to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 You got that sort of impression at that stage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were any of your homes rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I wouldn't know - really. I should think the - first three were, but I wouldn't know anything about the landlord or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember feeling that your parents ever had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
I don't feel that but - I think money was pretty short. Later on at Burstall, I know why - looking back. It was because father was saving up so hard to put -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So you weren't basically hard up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Not really, we didn't have money. And the boys certainly didn't have enough.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
When there was someone in the district whom people disapproved of very strongly, was there a special way in which they showed it? Did you ever come across something called rough music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh no. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember anything about an effigy being made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were you given lessons by either of your parents or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No. Taught to knit by - Auntie Pam. And basket weaving, before it was done at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How old were you when you first started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I think I must have been about five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How many schools did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Does that include School of Art or - I was - I went to - three. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember when you changed schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I should think probably five to six and a half, something. And six and a half 'til - eight and a half. Wiggeston.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I went - fourteen - trying to think, I - I would - I think I'd go in the September and I'd be nine in the October. At seven -
 trying to think - fourteen, if - I think I'd be seventeen when I left. Seventeen. And fifteen - fifteen to - comes a bit wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When you first started school what time did you go in the morning and when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Was there afternoon school at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I should doubt it. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What sort of school was the first school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well it was a - a lovely old house rather like this, in Belgrave. And I can still visualize the schoolmistress. Now -
 looking back, she was a real lady. It was a day school. Boys and girls, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 And your parents paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 You don't know how much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No. Don't think it would be much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How did you get to school at that stage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well I remember walking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you know how long it took you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I should think about ten minutes or quarter of an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Nobody.
