There was - there were two who were different. Sort of strict. Stricter than the others, but I remember one of the mistresses saying, you know nobody liked t
hese strict ones, when we were young, but - I remember - another mistress saying it made life very much easier for her, as she didn't have to be so strict. Because these other two were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did these teachers emphasise certain things as important in life?
