I've forgotten really, breaking rules and - you also showed her - your excellence, if you had an essay marked excellent - and if - if you got so many order marks it meant a conduct mark or something like that but - I
've really forgotten - for talking and leaving things about in the school or - not changing your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6301663\charrsid11354935 slippers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
 and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did your parents show an interest in your work at this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did they ask what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes. They'd got games days and - you know, sort of physical - you know, when you all do drill, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 prize givings}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 . They were quite something. Oh yes.
