\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I think there was more of a mix up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did the teachers there single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No.
