\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were there any gangs or groups in that school?
