Yes. But - you know you sort of read about people getting - a thrill out of it, I don't think I did. As I say - it was my duty. I think it is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did most of your friends as far as you know?
