\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I would.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Would the children share a bed or a bedroom?
