\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh when they needed them, we were more civilised then. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12785957\charrsid11354935 
I probably only changed your - woollen combies and vest once a week.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
