Say we'd have a proper breakfast, and then - early days at Bedford Alan came home for a midday meal which was a more important one. And then - well you'd be so little you see, we'd have - you'd have tea and then I think I'd put you to bed a
nd then we'd have - sort of scrambled eggs and that sort of thing for the evening meal. Something light.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Where were meals eaten?
