\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well I'd just tell you, I don't remember punishing you, do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I remember getting the hairbrush once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I thought that was Pam. Pam - it did Pam good, I don't know whether it did you good. It did - did Pam and the world of good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you remember in general about punishments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Was it mostly you who'd tell us off or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh I would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Do you ever remember a particular occasion when you punished them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No, I - I say I remember hairbrushing Pam. But - I think it was a sort of hysteria becaus
e she said - I'm good now mummy, you see, and stopped it. But I don't remember spanking you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I remember once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What was it for?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Squabbling with Pam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I did you both them I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Would you say that your children received the idea
s they had about how to behave from both parents or did one of you play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What do you think? I think - I - quietly what I said went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When your children had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 My children? Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Can you say in what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well how old would you want the children to be? Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When did birthdays start being different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well I don't think they bothered much when we were children, but when you were children
 - well surely we had a birthday cake and presents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When your children were children when did you start celebrating birthdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Always. I think. Oh I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So they did have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Anything different to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I - birthday cake. Probably just a little homemade one, something very simple.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 If there were - any other babies, I seem to remember having - a baby of your age when we lived in Bedford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Can you remember anything you did with your husband and children on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes, always stockings. And - presents. Not Christmas trees 'til later I think. We decorated the house of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Even at Bedford?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Who played it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Husband - Alan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did any of you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Only Scottish student songs. And Gilbert and Sullivan. Oh now - later on - I had singing lessons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Is this before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 No. It was before 1922.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you play any games with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I expect so. Ring o' ring o' roses and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did your husband join in the games or play different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 If he was at home. Of course you see the children were so young, there was no tennis then or anyth
ing like that, that came later. The baby - baby things - baby games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were there books in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I suppose so. And we - shared magazines with - Alan's - you know, fellow engineers. Quite g
ood ones. Like the Connoisseur and things like that we used to - hand them round, you know, they were bought monthly and - I don't know which we kept, I expect one lot would keep one and one another. But I do remember sharing magazines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Where did the books come from?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I don't think we belonged to a library at Bedford. But - I expect we bought them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 You don't think you did belong to a library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Don't think so there, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you read aloud to each other or to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes, Alan used to read - Sherlock Holmes to me and got across 'cos I guessed the end always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When he was reading aloud were you sort of doing something at the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I expect I was sewing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were the children taken out visiting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Who took them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Were they taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh sometimes we both took them. Oh, yes. I'd wheel you in a pram and do the shopping always. Very proudly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did the children ever go out just with their father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I don't think so. He didn't have much time you know. This is wartime. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What did you do on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
Well before you came we used to - and there was only one year, we cycled out - you know and took a picnic. Oh and then we took you on the fron
t of the bicycle too. Yes, don't you remember? We had a little seat at the front of Alan's bicycle. There wasn't so much traffic then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What did you do in the early years for holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well - the first year - you arrived - the children arrived, we went to this farm at Sandy.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 How long would that be for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Fortnight I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Why did you choose to go to Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Because it was easy and there was a war on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you get a holiday every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 In the beginning years were they always the same sort of holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Well - later we went - to the seaside, to Herne Bay or - Gorleston.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What sort of activities happened on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Padding. No, we just loved the sea and the freedom of the - sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you all go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did extra people go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes, granny - went - you know, Granny Thwaites mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 On holidays? Or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When you first had children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
Well Alan worked in the morning. Oh yes. Always. And we'd have Saturday afternoon where we'd probably go for - cycle ride into the country and - might have tea at a - cottage. But that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 What about Sundays, how did you spend Sundays?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 
We didn't go to church in those days. At all at Bedford. This is when we had children of course. Oh just went for jolly - long walks I think - and gardened. And I had an allotment at Bedfo
rd I remember. Yes. I ought to have remembered that before. Because in the very early married days we had allotment, I - forgotten for how long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 So you would have done that on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you or the children put on different clothes on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 When I was young we did but I don't think we did when you were young, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you think it was wrong to work or to enjoy yourself on a Sunday or did you think it didn't matter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 I thought it didn't matter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid210235 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Did you allow the children to play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1841092 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11753691\charrsid11354935 Yes.
